briefdescription.para: Create new MET object from sum of two MissingET_v1 objects.

detaileddescription.para: The MET components of the two referenced objects are added by (1) creating a copy of the first referenced MET object and (2) use the xAOD::MissingET_v1::operator+=(const xAOD::MissingET_v1&) method to add the second referenced MET object to it.

simplesect.para: New MissingET_v1 object reflecting the result of the add operation.

parameterdescription.para: reference to non-modifiable first MET object
reference to non-modifiable second MET object

briefdescription.para: Create new MET object from difference between two MissingET_v1 objects.

detaileddescription.para: The MET components of the two referenced objects are subtracted by (1) creating a copy of the first referenced MET object and (2) use the xAOD::MissingET_v1::operator-=(const xAOD::MissingET_v1&) method to subtract the second referenced MET object from it.

simplesect.para: New MissingET_v1 object reflecting the result of the subtract operation.

parameterdescription.para: reference to non-modifiable first MET object
reference to non-modifiable second MET object

briefdescription.para: Create new MET object from source with scaled (weighted) kinematics.

detaileddescription.para: The kinematic components of the referenced MET objects are scaled by (1) creating a copy of the referenced MET object and (2) use the xAOD::MissingET_v1::operator*=(double) method to apply the scale to the components of the new MET object.

simplesect.para: New MissingET_v1 object reflecting the result of the multiply operation.

briefdescription.para: Create new MET object from source with scaled (weighted) kinematics.
Create new MET object from source with scaled kinematics.

detaileddescription.para: The kinematic components of the referenced MET objects are scaled by (1) creating a copy of the referenced MET object and (2) use the xAOD::MissingET_v1::operator/=(double) method to divide the components of the new MET object by the scale factor.

simplesect.para: New MissingET_v1 object reflecting the result of the divide operation.
